            "24x24": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452",
            "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452",
            "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"
          },
          "displayName": "BoYang",
          "active": true,
          "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
        },
        "created": "2014-09-05T23:38:15.390+0000",
        "updated": "2014-09-05T23:38:15.390+0000"
      },
      {
        "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12739630/comment/14125797",
        "id": "14125797",
        "author": {
          "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=aw",
          "name": "aw",
          "key": "aw",
          "avatarUrls": {
            "48x48": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681",
            "24x24": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681",
            "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681",
            "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681"
          },
          "displayName": "Allen Wittenauer",
          "active": true,
          "timeZone": "America/Tijuana"
        },
        "body": "This is pretty much incompatible with security. So it should probably fail the nodemanager process under that condition.",
        "updateAuthor": {
          "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=aw",
          "name": "aw",
          "key": "aw",
          "avatarUrls": {
            "48x48": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681",
            "24x24": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681",
            "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681",
            "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681"
          },
          "displayName": "Allen Wittenauer",
          "active": true,
          "timeZone": "America/Tijuana"
        },
        "created": "2014-09-08T17:38:18.402+0000",
        "updated": "2014-09-08T17:38:18.402+0000"
      },
      {
        "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12739630/comment/14125834",
        "id": "14125834",
        "author": {
          "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=bobyangbo",
          "name": "bobyangbo",
          "key": "bobyangbo",
          "avatarUrls": {
            "48x48": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452",
            "24x24": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452",
            "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452",
            "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"
          },
          "displayName": "BoYang",
          "active": true,
          "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
        },
        "body": "In my rough testing, it did not fail the node manager process. In my Container Executor implementation (launchContainer method), I register a new application master, send a message to another long running process, and unregister the application master. I can see the application finished successfully.\n\nOf course, that was my very draft initial testing. We could fine-tune the code to make it work better. But technically it seems doable now. Thus I am curious whether the YARN community could take this feature and provide official support.",
        "updateAuthor": {
          "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=bobyangbo",
          "name": "bobyangbo",
          "key": "bobyangbo",
          "avatarUrls": {
            "48x48": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452",
            "24x24": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452",
            "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452",
            "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"
          },
          "displayName": "BoYang",
          "active": true,
          "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
        },
        "created": "2014-09-08T18:06:55.660+0000",
        "updated": "2014-09-08T18:06:55.660+0000"
      },
      {
        "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12739630/comment/14125838",
        "id": "14125838",
        "author": {
          "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=aw",
          "name": "aw",
          "key": "aw",
          "avatarUrls": {
            "48x48": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681",
            "24x24": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681",
            "16x16": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681",
            "32x32": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681"
          },
          "displayName": "Allen Wittenauer",
          "active": true,
          "timeZone": "America/Tijuana"
        },
        "body": "Sorry, I wasn't clear:  if this feature goes in, it must fail the nodemanager process if security is enabled due to running tasks as the yarn user being extremely insecure.",
        "updateAuthor": {
          "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=aw",
          "name": "aw",
          "key": "aw",
          "avatarUrls": {
